-- India's Infosys shares fall 3 pct as founders said to sell shares
-- By Indulal PM
-- Sun Dec 07, 2014 10:43PM EST
-- None



MUMBAI, Dec 8 (Reuters) - Shares in India's Infosys Ltd <INFY.NS> fell 3 percent in pre-open trading on Monday following reports that some of its founders were selling shares in the software services exporter worth $1.1 billion

